   <text>
    <body>
      <pb n="1"/>
      <div type="Paragraph">
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_1"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">Kungs Lohder Mahzitais pee Jehkaba</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_2"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">Baſnizu Rihgâ.</div>
      </div>
      <div type="Paragraph">
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_3"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">Zeenigs Tehtiht un Mahmina !</div>
      </div>
      <div type="Paragraph">
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_4"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">Es eſmu ſenn, un daudſreiſi us jums gribbejis rakſtiht,</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_5"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">bet tas naw gaddijees, ka man weens ustizzams</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_6"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">draugs buhtu Rihga nahzis, kas pee jums warretu</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_7"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">eenahkt: Tad nu luhdſu juhs Sirds</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_8"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">ſemmigi, ne ņemmeet par ļaunu kad es pee</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_9"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">jums rakſtu.</div>
      </div>
      <div type="Paragraph">
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_10"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">Es pateizu jums tuhkſtoſchkahrt ſirds mihligi</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_11"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">un paſemmigi, par juhſu mihleſtibu</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_12"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">un labbu pamahziſchanu, ka juhs bijaht</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_13"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">isgahjuſchu ſeemâ mannu dehlu pamahziſchi,</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_14"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">ka mann to unniverſahl Plahſteri</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_15"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">buhs bruhkeht: wehl ſewiſķi pateizu</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_16"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">par to mihļu padohmiņu, ko juhs man tai</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_17"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">laikâ bijaht lihdſ rakſtijuſchi. Es eſmu</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_18"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">nu to plahſteri bruhkejis lihdſ ſcho laiku,</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_19"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">Tas irr man tak daudſ labbi darrijis</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_20"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">bet wehl gann irr wahjibas un gruhtumi</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_21"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">juhtami. Es gann gribbetu to Plahſteri</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_22"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">daudſ bruhkeht, un allaſchin no <corr>jauna</corr><sic>nojauna</sic></div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_1_23"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">us likt, bet tik daudſ ne ſpehju makſaht</div>
      </div>
      <pb n="2"/>
      <div type="Paragraph">
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_1"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">Tad nu tahdehļ, wehl mihļi luhdſohs, kad</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_2"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">juhs man wehl par 2. Dalderi ta plahſtera</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_3"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">warretu doht, jo tas irr tak preekſch man</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_4"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">gauſchi derrigs. To ween luhdſohs, zeeniga</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_5"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">Mahmina ! Kad juhs man warretu no labba</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_6"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">jauna ſtippra plahſtera isdoht? Par to</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_7"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">es jums ſewiſki ſirds mihligi pateikſchu:</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_8"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">un kad man mihlais &lt;sirds> no ſcha wahjuma</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_9"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">weenreiſ ahra palihdſ, tad es juhs ne aismirſiſchu,</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_10"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">bet dohmaju wehl juhs atmiñeht,</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_11"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">un jums no ſchehliga deewa puſſes wiſſu</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_12"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">labbu laimi un klahſchanu wehleju.</div>
      </div>
      <div type="Paragraph">
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_13"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">No tahm Trappehm un Pillehm juhs man</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_14"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">ne ko dohdeet, tahs man ne ko palihdſ. Tas</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_15"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">Mihlz eſſentz <corr>man</corr><sic>nan</sic> ne kahdu Lakſeer irr darrijis,</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_16"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">es eſmu winna eekſch tukſchu Mahgu pa</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_17"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">ſeptin reiſi eenehmis, bet man tak ne lakſeereja:</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_18"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">Jo es ſew eſmu zittu lakſeer daſchu</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_19"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">reiſi eenehmis, mans wehders irr nu gann</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_20"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">walligs. To</div>
       <div type="Language" lang="Latin">eſſentia amara,</div>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">un</div>
       <div type="Language" lang="Latin">eſſentia</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_21"/>
       <div type="Language" lang="Latin">dulcis</div>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">ar ne waijaga, tas gann irr</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_22"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">druſzin labbags, bet es ne ſpehju tik</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_2_23"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">daudſ makſaht. Tapehz es ween gribbu</div>
      </div>
      <pb n="3"/>
      <div type="Paragraph">
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_3_1"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">pee ta Plahſtera palikt, un to no jums</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_3_2"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">gaidiht.</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_3_3"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">Dſihwojeet ar Deewu ! Lai jums ar winnu</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_3_4"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">labbi klahjahs. Un daudſ labbu deenu</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_3_5"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">weſſelibu, un labb' klahſchanu, jums</div>
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_3_6"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">wehleju juhsu nammâ.</div>
      </div>
      <div type="Paragraph">
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_3_7"/>
        <div type="Language" lang="Latvian">ſilla ſemneek Anſch.</div>
      </div>
      <div type="Paragraph">
       <lb id="V1771_SZA_3_8"/>
       <div type="Language" lang="Latin">d/. 11. Junij. 1771.</div>
      </div>
